{"tid":1134960,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"法改會倡立窺淫、偷影裙底罪　張達明：適用對象無分男女","createTime":"2019-05-02T04:27:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-02T04:27:49.000Z","uid":241764,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"5c4a8a106f58de56086420fe0789b2c657447053","tid":1134960,"uid":241764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T04:27:49.000Z","msg":"法改會早前發表報告書，建議新訂窺淫罪及未經同意下拍攝裙底罪。法改會性罪行檢討小組委員會委員張達明接受港台節目訪問時表示，如一般香港婦女都會選擇在育嬰室或隱蔽地方哺乳，他們有合理期望保障私隱，故有關偷拍或偷窺的行為均涉「窺淫罪」；然而如婦女選擇在眾目睽睽地方哺乳，現時建議的兩個罪行難規管。<br />\n<br />\n張達明承認在的士行為被偷拍或偷窺有灰色地帶，建議政府考慮針對有關情況修改的士附例規管，以免法改會建議的兩條罪行涵蓋範圍太闊會誤中副車、過猶不及。<br />\n<br />\n另外，張達明強調罪行適用對象原則上是無分男女，所謂的「未經同意下拍攝裙底」純粹是容易表述的簡稱，並非未來制定法律的用語。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20190502/s00001/1556763510508/%E6%B3%95%E6%94%B9%E6%9C%83%E5%80%A1%E7%AB%8B%E7%AA%BA%E6%B7%AB-%E5%81%B7%E5%BD%B1%E8%A3%99%E5%BA%95%E7%BD%AA-%E5%BC%B5%E9%81%94%E6%98%8E-%E9%81%A9%E7%94%A8%E5%B0%8D%E8%B1%A1%E7%84%A1%E5%88%86%E7%94%B7%E5%A5%B3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20190502%2Fs00001%2F1556763510508%2F%25E6%25B3%2595%25E6%2594%25B9%25E6%259C%2583%25E5%2580%25A1%25E7%25AB%258B%25E7%25AA%25BA%25E6%25B7%25AB-%25E5%2581%25B7%25E5%25BD%25B1%25E8%25A3%2599%25E5%25BA%2595%25E7%25BD%25AA-%25E5%25BC%25B5%25E9%2581%2594%25E6%2598%258E-%25E9%2581%25A9%25E7%2594%25A8%25E5%25B0%258D%25E8%25B1%25A1%25E7%2584%25A1%25E5%2588%2586%25E7%2594%25B7%25E5%25A5%25B3&d=P2v3VPQ3iBAPr6cjv61qmX4HMPoqNxaa4E9h32y1mRE%3D&h=2703e5a4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20190502%2Fs00001%2F1556763510508%2F%25E6%25B3%2595%25E6%2594%25B9%25E6%259C%2583%25E5%2580%25A1%25E7%25AB%258B%25E7%25AA%25BA%25E6%25B7%25AB-%25E5%2581%25B7%25E5%25BD%25B1%25E8%25A3%2599%25E5%25BA%2595%25E7%25BD%25AA-%25E5%25BC%25B5%25E9%2581%2594%25E6%2598%258E-%25E9%2581%25A9%25E7%2594%25A8%25E5%25B0%258D%25E8%25B1%25A1%25E7%2584%25A1%25E5%2588%2586%25E7%2594%25B7%25E5%25A5%25B3&h=6e34eeac\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20190502/s00001/1556763510508/%E6%B3%95%E6%94%B9%E6%9C%83%E5%80%A1%E7%AB%8B%E7%AA%BA%E6%B7%AB-%E5%81%B7%E5%BD%B1%E8%A3%99%E5%BA%95%E7%BD%AA-%E5%BC%B5%E9%81%94%E6%98%8E-%E9%81%A9%E7%94%A8%E5%B0%8D%E8%B1%A1%E7%84%A1%E5%88%86%E7%94%B7%E5%A5%B3</a>"}]}